cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.CR 

This paper is about deep learning-based face recognition, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper proposes a new loss function for training deep neural networks, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The proposed method is evaluated on large-scale face verification and identification datasets, which involves multimedia processing (cs.MM) and potentially computer security (cs.CR).
